title: Why Do Noises Other People Make Seem Louder Than Our Own?
itunes:title: Why Do Noises Other People Make Seem Louder Than Our Own?
description:
Humans and other animals tend to tune out the noises they themselves make. Learn how and why this happens in today's episode of BrainStuff.
